        </figure>
        <para>
            <hotlnk xrefid="f1401545">ZTSE2847 Yoke Remover, Bar Type</hotlnk>
            - A yoke remover tool for extracting shaft end yokes on rear axles having an interference fit between the
            yoke and the axle input or output splined shaft.
        </para>
        <figure id="f1401545" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1401545" filename="../figg14/G1401545.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="152px"
                     scalefitheight="192px" resolution="72"/>
            <caption>Figure 45. ZTSE2847 Yoke Remover, Bar Type</caption>
        </figure>
        <para>
            <hotlnk xrefid="f1401546">ZTSE4335 Installer, Differential Yoke</hotlnk>
            - 1 1/2" - 12 and 1 1/4" - 12. Used for the installation of the end yoke onto the splines of the pinion,
            input, output or through shaft. This tool presses the yoke in place with forcing screw action, eliminating
            costly part damage.
        </para>
        <figure id="f1401546" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1401546" filename="../figg14/G1401546.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="152px"
                     scalefitheight="152px" resolution="72"/>
            <caption>Figure 46. ZTSE4335 Installer, Differential Yoke</caption>
        </figure>
        <para>
            <hotlnk xrefid="f1401547">Torque Multipliers</hotlnk>
        </para>
        <para>These powerful Torque Multipliers are designed as general all - purpose utility tools. They provide the
            necessary power to tighten threaded fasteners such as nuts, bolts, cap screws, etc.
        </para>
        <figure id="f1401547" figsize="pg-wide">
            <graphic id="g1401547" filename="../figg14/G1401547.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="392px"
                     scalefitheight="312px" resolution="72"/>
            <caption>Figure 47. Torque Multipliers</caption>
        </figure>
